```
pip install airflow-azure-sso

from airflow_azure_sso import generate_airflow_config

generate_airflow_config(
    client_id="<client_id>",
    tenant_id="<tenant_id>",
    client_secret="<client_secret>",

    airflow_config_file="<airflow_config_file>",
)
